{
  "stem": "11472.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then he'll come in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were so fortunate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were safe underneath.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the men were very, very-- a few times-- the police were watching us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A few times, they were in the fields, and they were shooting after them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The men would go out and bring in-- one night when it was stormy, when it was raining, my grandmother would figure out when, when the moon was not so high, they would go out to the forest, and they would bring in, they would cut up woods.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They would go-- when the, the peasants were digging potatoes, they would steal potatoes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "One night they would bring potatoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "All night, they would carry potatoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then the corn, then wheat, because we had our own mill.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This is unbelievable what these men did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Anyway, once they found out that we're there, everybody was afraid to be the first one to get out of the exit.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So my grandmother had another idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She made an effigy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She made a man.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She dressed up a man, like a scarecrow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She dressed up a man in a, in a suit with a hat and a stick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they would push out that man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And when they saw that nobody was shooting at them, the men would go out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Anyway, the only time we would sit and breathe, afraid to breathe, is when the men would be out, because it was very dangerous for them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We never knew if they'll come back or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "When they left, we never knew if they'll come back or not.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "This is already, I would say, I am now January or February 1944.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is what I'm telling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We come back.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
